Bubble Guru offers an embeddable video bubble for your website or your emails. Its service allows you to record short videos directly from
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Bubble Guru offers an embeddable video "bubble" for your website or your emails.  Its service allows you to record short videos directly from your computer's webcam and insert them over a webpage or through a link in an email.  Your video appears in a small bubble anywhere you want on the screen.  It floats above any original content so that you can add your videos without redesigning your web page.  Videos can play once or every time your page is refreshed.  Controls are shown with a mouseover of the video bubble.Bubble Guru does not require any software installation or downloads.  It works with your existing webcam and takes very little time to set up an account.  Premium accounts which provide you with space for up to 5 or 25 videos are offered for $10 and $40 dollars per month respectively.  With a premium account users can also upload their own videos and customize the shape of the bubble player.The service could potentially work well for Blogs, online tutorials or just as a fun extra on your personal site.  To add the video player site administrators need only to paste a few lines of code into their site.  Currently it is compatible with Wordpress, Blogger and TypePad blogs.Bubble Guru could become really addicting if you could add it to your favorite social network profiles or if it played videos directly from an opened email instead of providing a link to a new page.  It seems like a better app for non-professionals, but could certainly be used for more serious tasks.Bubble Guru doesn't have any direct competitors but is part of the personalized video channel field.  Other larger companies in this field include [BrightCove](http://crunchbase.com/organization/brightcove), [VideoEgg](http://crunchbase.com/organization/videoegg) and [PermissionTV](http://crunchbase.com/organization/permissiontv).

Industries: Drone Management, Drones, Oil and Gas
Description: We are developing intrinsically safe and EX-P drones for oil and gas inspections
Full Description: Tachyon Oil & Gas, inc. is focused on bringing responsibly safe drones for oil and gas inspection to market. We are developing a UL compliant drone that will be undergoing UL Intrinsically Safe certification testing that will resolve concerns over hot work permits and ignition safety on oil and gas drill floors and rig pads.  Current Drone Inspection services are unable to operate without a hot work permit or a work stoppage without endangering the lives of everyone on the rig. The solution to this is to use Intrinsically Safe or EX-P drones that allow the drilling and extraction operations to continue while the inspection flights take place.  We have planned for two drones to be developed:  The Canary This drone is being built to meet standards to operate in Hazardous Gas Area Zone 0 T4 classified location, primarily inside voids, tanks, and pipes. No longer will you have to shut down operations and gas check the area before doing visual inspections with UAV systems. Features:  HD/IR Camera  Remote gas detection The Warbler A large commercial drone, with advanced avionics, capable of operating in Class 1 locations. Tachyon Oil & Gas is currently building and testing a large-scale commercial drone specifically designed for operations within electrical hazardous locations. Features:  HD/IR Cameras  Remote gas detection  45 minute+ flight time  3+ mile range Our drones will be using several proprietary features that we intend to patent including the navigation system, the engines, and the power flow system.
Industry Groups: Consumer Electronics, Consumer Goods, Energy, Hardware, Natural Resources, Software

Description: Blockchain enabled lending technology
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Not an evolution, a revolution. BLENDINGHUB: Blockchain Lending Platform  A deceptively simple end-to-end process by which a loan can be digitally and securely applied for, underwritten and funded using blockchain technology. With proprietary technology and processes, the BLENDINGHUB blockchain lending process provides a lender with a seamless, transparent and incorruptible ecosystem through which it can directly collect information from a borrower, make a credit decision, fund a loan and store the collateral. This ecosystem utilizes a distributed ledger to record, encrypt and store each transaction and guarantee the validity of a transaction by recording it not only on a main register but a connected distributed system of registers, all of which are connected through a secure validation mechanism.The resulting process can originate a loan at virtually no cost. This means that markets previously under served due to origination costs instantly become untapped reservoirs of new potential borrowers. This is the definition of disruptive innovation.
